Carnival Eats - Season 2, Episode 10




From Golden State to Gizzards

The Sacramento County Fair in California's state capital is the launching pad for trend-setting fair food including the famous Jalapeno Cheese Skirt Burger. Next, he meets the locals at Gizzard Fest in Michigan where they're serving a donut to die for, and an Onion Dog as big as his head.




Original Air Date: 17-Sep-2015
